The Famalicão Open is a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 28 July to 3 August 2019 in Vila Nova de Famalicão, Portugal.

Players receive 90 minutes for the entire game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.fpx.pt
